    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a formidable driver\u2019s example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, the drivetrain delivers linear power through a factory limited-slip differential. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The suspension geometry remains tight, offering the communicative feedback and lateral grip expected of an M-engineered chassis. While displaying minor aesthetic wear consistent with its mileage, its mechanical vitals are robust, making it an ideal candidate for the spirited purist.",
