      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for 2017 Porsche Macan S in Jet Black Metallic. This vehicle offers a perfect blend of utility and sports-car DNA. The 3.0L Twin-Turbo V6 delivers power smoothly, and the PDK transmission shifts flawlessly. It has been strictly serviced at recommended intervals, with a fresh oil change and a clean bill of health on the braking system recently documented. The interior features premium black leather; the cabin is smoke-free and the upholstery is in great shape, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s entry bolster. All tech features, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and infotainment system, are fully operational. Externally, the car presents beautifully with a deep shine. While there are a handful of minor stone chips on the hood from highway driving, the body is free of any significant dings or scratches. The 19-inch wheels are fitted with high-quality tires that have significant life remaining. This is a reliable, turn-key luxury SUV ready for its next chapter.",
